metadata.name: Awakening Resonance
metadata.description:
ðŸ”¹ Timeless Love..

Some memories we have in our lives, leaves traces on heart. 
Throughout our lives, it is the love that keeps us alive. You may not change your past but memories will keep themselves as a part of yourself.

True love is immortal and eternal. Soul is eternal.
As you hold on to your inner treasure, you will find the balance of peace in your heart. 

The main emotional job of the heart is love. 
But heart is more than just the center of love, it is also the center of our being.
